=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180930164717oYdJOLxQ4f197Hg6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180930164717bVx4Ze8rcQwEAPkt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180930164718746Szm1DisZno0Tb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180930164718ciR5eYLoOHyCUWmI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180930164718jRc1YqLUmzx0KISW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809301647186An5dEkfwOIWZlbv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180930164718G6sv4Dwt9VSEyYbT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180930164719ut5Cy63TFvrGYM7b.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>Comme des Garçons 2019 春季成衣系列。</strong><br></p><p>与上一季相比，川久保玲的新系列色调要沉着很多：不再五彩缤纷，而是以黑、灰、白为主，点缀少量印花。秀场音乐也选择了嗓音低沉的 Tom Waits。</p><p>造型上，一些模特戴上了假肚子，凸显风衣或连衣裙腰部的那道开口，并且在概念上强调“母性”和“女性”的主题。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180930165129rnMTe7RWZxH9lvos.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180930165126u9tNV5IbUM0FsoPi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180930165126lJ3zntbs4rTYQFwy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180930165126IzwUL2ZnMpbXROPT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figu